value.name: Tell Me a Lie
value.overview: Fill your family cravings, resolve your family regrets, and create memories for you The cosplay office — opened! Saburo runs the office with his amazing makeup and voice changing skills, and starts a cohabitation life with Xiao Zhen, a girl from the Qiao family. Together, for every customer who spends a lot of money on the door, transform into the perfect stand-in they want to see the most… Saburo and his partners run a “Memory Temporary Agency” that turns lies into sweet dreams, but when the lies are exposed… Is the good memory deceived by the client, or is it not afraid to look directly at yourself in life?
